{
  "stem": "4963.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She didn't want to be separated from the child, so the Germans said, go, both of you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he was-- he knew that his wife wasn't there, so he married this lady, Lotte, and my-- my cousin was there and I was there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember Lotte was very nice to me, and she immediately called in a seamstress and-- and, you know, and had some clothes made for me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I felt I had three dresses or two dresses and shoes and I felt like I was really in a palace, you know, my own room, and I remember decorating it and wanting to be beautiful.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So you weren't going to go to Palestine?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Did you--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was on my way to Palestine, but we had to wait.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, this was January of 1946.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- there were-- the-- the-- the ship was going to go the-- what ship was it?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The I was supposed to be on the ship, and so my cousin and I, we would go into Munich and meet the Jewish community, you know, there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And incidentally, again I said, no, I have to go to school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I enrolled, and I-- I went to look for a German university, and-- and again, said I finished gymnasium, which I really didn't.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I just wanted to-- I knew that the only way I could get ahead was through education, and so I said, I have to arm myself with the best education I possibly can.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so anyhow, I-- I was on my way and waiting to go on that ship when my aunt got word and my aunt-- my uncle was also corresponding with my aunt in New York, my Aunt Assia, Assia Goder.",
      "word_count": 40
    }
  ],
